      <title>git</title>
      <link href="/2022/01/14/git/"/>
      <url>/2022/01/14/git/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="学习地址"><a href="#学习地址" class="headerlink" title="学习地址"></a>学习地址</h1><p><a href="https://learngitbranching.js.org/?locale=zh_CN">学git的网站</a></p><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/ShenQiXiaYang/article/details/110734627">git安装博客</a></p><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_36749906/article/details/113918554">git restore&#x2F; git rm</a></p><p><a href="https://git-scm.com/book/zh/v2">学git的书</a></p><hr><h1 id="一、版本控制"><a href="#一、版本控制" class="headerlink" title="一、版本控制"></a>一、版本控制</h1><ul><li><p>协同修改</p></li><li><p>数据备份</p></li><li><p>版本管理</p><p>SVN是增量式管理。git采取文件系统快照的方式</p></li><li><p>权限控制</p></li><li><p>历史记录</p></li><li><p>分支管理</p><p>允许开发团队在工作过程中多条生产线同时推进任务，提高效率</p></li></ul><h1 id="二、git简介"><a href="#二、git简介" class="headerlink" title="二、git简介"></a>二、git简介</h1><ul><li>工作区，用来写代码</li><li>本地库，临时存储</li><li>暂存区，历史版本</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">工作区 git add -&gt; 暂存区 git commit -&gt; 本地库</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>局域网环境下使用gitlab服务器，外网环境下 github和码云</p><h2 id="本地库和远程库"><a href="#本地库和远程库" class="headerlink" title="本地库和远程库"></a>本地库和远程库</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">团队内</span><br><span class="line">1、创建本地库push到远程库</span><br><span class="line">2、本地库从远程库clone到本地</span><br><span class="line">3、本地库push（加入团队）到远程库</span><br><span class="line">4、从远程库pull在创建者的本地库</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">跨团队</span><br><span class="line">1、从远程库fork（相当于复制）一个新的远程库</span><br><span class="line">2、从新的远程库clone到本地库</span><br><span class="line">3、从本地库push到新的远程库</span><br><span class="line">4、新的远程库 pull request，然后审核，再merge到原本的远程库</span><br><span class="line">5、原本的远程库成员就可以pull到自己的本地</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="三、git命令行"><a href="#三、git命令行" class="headerlink" title="三、git命令行"></a>三、git命令行</h1><h2 id="本地库操作"><a href="#本地库操作" class="headerlink" title="本地库操作"></a>本地库操作</h2><ul><li><p>本地库初始化</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git init 初始化 //.git是隐藏文件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>设置签名</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">* 形式：</span><br><span class="line">    用户名：tom</span><br><span class="line">    email地址：goodMorning@gmail.com</span><br><span class="line">* 作用：区分不同开发人员的身份</span><br><span class="line">* 辨析：这里设置的签名和登录远程库（代码托管中心）的账号、密码没有任何关系</span><br><span class="line">* 命令：</span><br><span class="line">    项目级别/仓库级别：仅在当前本地库范围有效</span><br><span class="line">        git config user.name tom_pro</span><br><span class="line">        git config user.email goodMoring_pro@gmail.com</span><br><span class="line">        信息保存位置 ./.git/config</span><br><span class="line">    系统用户级别：windows系统用户范围</span><br><span class="line">        git config --global user.name tom_glb</span><br><span class="line">        git config --global user.email goodMoring_glb@gmail.com</span><br><span class="line">        信息保存位置 ~/.gitconfig文件</span><br><span class="line">    级别优先级：就近原则，项目级别优先于系统用户级别</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>基本操作</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git status //查看状态</span><br><span class="line">git add good.txt //追踪一个文件</span><br><span class="line">vim good.txt</span><br><span class="line">ESC + : wq //保存退出</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git restore --staged &lt;file&gt; // git add的撤回</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git commit good.txt</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">:set nu //显示行号</span><br><span class="line">i 进入vim编辑</span><br><span class="line">cat good.txt //查看文件信息</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">初次追踪用git add，更新也可以git add / git commit -a</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git commit -m“消息” good.txt //可以不用进vim编辑器写了</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">小结</span><br><span class="line">git status //查看状态，查看工作区、暂存区的状态</span><br><span class="line">git add [file name]//添加操作，将工作区的新建/修改添加到暂存区</span><br><span class="line">git commit -m &quot;commit message&quot; [file name] //提交操作，将暂存区的内容提交到本地库</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>查看历史记录</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git log //查看历史记录，最完整的形式</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">会出现很多条记录按空格进入下一页，按q退出回到git控制端</span><br><span class="line">即多屏显示控制方式：空格向下翻页，b向上翻页，q退出</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git log --pretty=oneline //日志一行输出</span><br><span class="line">git log --oneline //哈希值只显示一部分</span><br><span class="line">git reflog //有队列编号，方便回退历史版本</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>前进和后退历史记录</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git有一个指针HEAD</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">有三种：1、基于索引值操作（推荐） 2、使用^符号（异或） 3、使用~符号</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git reset --hard [局部索引值]</span><br><span class="line">***选中即复制了，直接粘贴***</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git reset --hard HEAD^</span><br><span class="line">使用^:只能后退，一个^后退一次，n个^后退n次</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git reset --hard HEAD~3</span><br><span class="line">使用~:波浪线后面的数字代表后退几步</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure> <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git help reset //查看reset具体的命令</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">--soft //仅仅在本地库移动HEAD指针，不碰工作区和暂存区</span><br><span class="line">--mixed //在本地库移动HEAD指针，重置暂存区</span><br><span class="line">--hard //暂存区和工作区都重置</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">前进和后退会出现多个HEAD，当前的HEAD看commit的那几条</span><br><span class="line">后退之后，status会变绿，本地库后退，显得暂存区向前了</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">使用mixed，status会变红</span><br><span class="line">使用hard，本地库，暂存区和工作区一起后退，不会变绿变红</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>删除文件</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rm [文件名] //删除文件</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">完整流程</span><br><span class="line">rm aaa.txt</span><br><span class="line">git add aaa.txt</span><br><span class="line">git status //这样红色的删除文件会变成绿色的删除文件</span><br><span class="line">git commit -m &quot;delete aaa.txt&quot; aaa.txt</span><br><span class="line">//本地库会有一条这样的记录，git只会增加记录，不会删除记录</span><br><span class="line">其实并没有删除，可以回退到原来的版本</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>删除文件并找回</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">前提：删除前，文件存在时的状态提交到了本地库</span><br><span class="line">操作：git reset --hard [指针位置]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>比较文件</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git diff [文件名]</span><br><span class="line">显示的红色是删除的行，绿色是增加的行</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">添加到暂存区，再使用diff会发现没有区别</span><br><span class="line">若使用 git diff HEAD^ apple.txt又可以看见差异了</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">小结：</span><br><span class="line">git diff [文件名] 将工作区的文件和暂存区进行比较</span><br><span class="line">git diff[本地库中历史版本][文件名] 与历史版本比较</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git diff //不加文件名，会比较多个文件的差异</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>分支管理</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">不在主干上（main）开发，创建一个分支（feature_blue，feature_game）</span><br><span class="line">各个分支之间是独立的,方便试错，可以删除不影响主干</span><br><span class="line">合并对主干来说是大升级，若主干又bug，创建一个hot_fix分支（热修复），修复完再合并到主干</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git branch -v //查看所有分支</span><br><span class="line">git branch hot_fix //创建hot_fix分支</span><br><span class="line">git checkout hot_fix //转到hot_fix分支</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">创建分支：git branch [分支名]</span><br><span class="line">查看分支：git branch -v</span><br><span class="line">切换分支：git checkout [分支名]</span><br><span class="line">合并分支：第一步切换到接受修改的分支上，第二部执行merge命令</span><br><span class="line">    git checkout main</span><br><span class="line">    git merge hot_fix</span><br><span class="line">解决冲突：进入文件可以看见冲突内容，如下：</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt; HEAD</span><br><span class="line">edit by hot_fix</span><br><span class="line">=======</span><br><span class="line">edit by main</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; main</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">冲突后，在vim编辑器编辑好，退出</span><br><span class="line">git status //查看状态会出现红色信息</span><br><span class="line">git add good.txt //解决了冲突，但仍处在合并的状态</span><br><span class="line">git commit -m &quot;XX&quot; //一定不能带文件名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="远程库操作"><a href="#远程库操作" class="headerlink" title="远程库操作"></a>远程库操作</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir huashan //创建新文件夹</span><br><span class="line">cd huashan</span><br><span class="line">git init</span><br><span class="line">vim huashanjianfa.txt</span><br><span class="line">git add huashanjianfa.txt</span><br><span class="line">git commit -m &quot;test github&quot; huashanjianfa.txt</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git remote -v //查看远程库列表</span><br><span class="line">git remote add origin https://github.com/yilan0916/huashan.git //origin是别名</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">克隆远程库</span><br><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/yilan0916/huashan.git</span><br><span class="line">1、下载到本地     2、创建远origin程地址别名    3、初始化本地库</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pull = fetch + merge</span><br><span class="line">具体操作</span><br><span class="line">git fetch origin main //下载到本地，但未修改本地文件</span><br><span class="line">cat huashanjianfa.txt</span><br><span class="line">git checkout origin/main //不是本地，是下载的</span><br><span class="line">cat huashanjianfa.txt //发现文件变了</span><br><span class="line">git checkout main //切回本地</span><br><span class="line">git merge origin/main //合并</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">or git pull origin main</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">小结</span><br><span class="line">pull=fetch+merge</span><br><span class="line">git fetch [远程库地址别名] [远程分支名]</span><br><span class="line">git merge [远程库地址别名/远程分支名]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git pull [远程库地址别名] [远程分支名]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>解决冲突</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1、如果不是基于GitHub远程库的最新版所做的修改，不能推送，必须先拉去</span><br><span class="line">2、拉去下来如果进入冲突状态，则按照”分支冲突解决“操作解决即可</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="跨团队"><a href="#跨团队" class="headerlink" title="跨团队"></a>跨团队</h1><h1 id="四、gitlab服务器环境搭建"><a href="#四、gitlab服务器环境搭建" class="headerlink" title="四、gitlab服务器环境搭建"></a>四、gitlab服务器环境搭建</h1><h1 id="五、git图形化界面操作"><a href="#五、git图形化界面操作" class="headerlink" title="五、git图形化界面操作"></a>五、git图形化界面操作</h1>]]></content>
      
      
